Yesterday we celebrated the listing of the Bitwise Aptos Staking ETP, $APTB _

@moshaikhs  and @HHorsley , the Founders and CEOs of @Aptos and @BitwiseInvest , rang the @sixgroup closing bell in Zurich to mark this milestone.

@Aptos , a high-performance L1 blockchain, has attracted attention from financial institutions and consumer brands for its innovative infrastructure and 8M+ monthly active users.

This ETP highlights Bitwise's leadership in providing investors access to cutting-edge opportunities in the evolving crypto asset class.

We're grateful to our clients and partners for their trust and support as we work to be the best partner in digital asset investments.

@moshaikhs  @HHorsley @BradleyDukeBTC  @SolomonTesfaye_  @Aptos   @BitwiseInvest @Bitwise_Europe  @sixgroup @CoinbaseInsto  

Not investment advice. For professional investors only. Capital at risk.

